data.description: Welcome Home to your cozy new abode in The Coves of San Jacinto CA! Become enchanted with your 4 bedroom 3 bath property, boasting over 2200 square feet of living space. You'll be pleased with all of the designer features such as formal entry with extended hallway, freshly painted interior walls in neutral tone, modern wood planking, paid off solar panels and much more. It has an open concept floor plan and the family room opens up to the well equipped kitchen furnished in stainless steel appliances, white shaker cabinets, pantry for storage and eat in breakfast nook with bar height counter space. A rare but valuable addition to the main floor of this home is a full bedroom and bathroom creating a wonderful guest suite downstairs. Upstairs you'll be greeted by a spacious and comfortable loft with natural lighting beaming in from the windows. Down the hall from the loft is the spacious master ensuite with walk in closet, dual vanity in the bathroom, shower-tub combo and water room. There are two additional guest bedrooms on the second floor plus a laundry for your convenience. The exterior of the home is a clean slate ready for the landscape design of your dreams, this approximately 6500 square foot lot has plenty of backyard space for a garden, pool and spa or outdoor kitchen! The home is secure with a Vivint alarm system and energy efficient with solar panels powered by Sun Power. The Cove community is home to beautiful parks and recreation which makes this neighborhood so peaceful. Don't miss your opportunity to schedule a private tour of this turnkey property, it will not last long on the market!! CALL TODAY.
